elements biblioid biblioid Element
biblioid &biblioid.purpose;
&biblioid.synopsis.gen;
Description
A bibliographic identifier, such as an ISBN number, Library of Congress identifier, or URI.
This element supercedes the isbn, issn, and pubsnumber elements.
Processing expectations
&format.inline; &format.csuppress;
&biblioid.parents.gen; &biblioid.children.gen;
Attributes
class
Identifies the encoding scheme of the identifier.
otherclass
Identifies the encoding scheme of the identifier when class is other.
See Also &biblioid.seealso.gen;
